'''Scout媒體'''是一間綜合性的體育媒體公司，主要是透過[[網站|網站]]發布消息<ref name="scout1">{{cite web |url=http://www.scout.com/3/company.html |title=Company Overview |publisher=Scout.com |date= |accessdate=June 11, 2013 |archive-date=2015-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150331003533/http://www.scout.com/3/company.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年，[[Fox_Sports|Fox Sports]]將它賣給[[North_American_Membership_Group|North American Membership Group]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://allthingsd.com/20131121/namg-confirms-it-has-bought-scout-from-fox-networks-group-in-content-roll-up-bid/ |title=NAMG Confirms It Has Bought Scout From Fox Networks Group in Dude-Focused Content Roll-Up Bid |accessdate=2015-04-11 |archive-date=2013-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131123073810/http://allthingsd.com/20131121/namg-confirms-it-has-bought-scout-from-fox-networks-group-in-content-roll-up-bid/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。對於大學球員的評價有一定的參考性。

==網路行銷==
旗下擁有超過300個網站，涵蓋包括高中、大學及職業<ref>{{cite web |url=http://newscorp.com/2012/06/28/news-corporation-announces-intent-to-pursue-separation-of-businesses-to-enhance-strategic-alignment-and-increase-operational-flexibility/ |title=FIM acquisition of Scout.com |publisher=http://newscorp.com/ |date= |accessdate=November 19, 2013 |archive-date=2015-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414081225/http://newscorp.com/2012/06/28/news-corporation-announces-intent-to-pursue-separation-of-businesses-to-enhance-strategic-alignment-and-increase-operational-flexibility/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

